title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses some of the notable names that are joining the LIV Tour. The guys play 'Good Idea or Bad Idea.' Plus, Reggie Miller explains why Draymond Green would be fine if he played in the 80's/90's.
